Well the good news is that most physici@@ ans in this case decided to pull the patient and try the i@@ bu@@ prof@@ en .
Very good for the physici@@ ans .
The other group of the physici@@ ans , they said , &quot; Y@@ est@@ er@@ day when you re@@ viewed the case you discovered there were two medic@@ ations you didn &apos;t try out yet , i@@ bu@@ prof@@ en and pi@@ ro@@ x@@ ic@@ am . &quot;
And they said , &quot; You have two medic@@ ations you didn &apos;t try out yet . What do you do ?
