Let &apos;s go for hip replac@@ ement . &quot;
I &apos;ll give you a couple of more examples on ir@@ rational deci@@ sion@@ -making .
Imagine I give you a choice .
Do you want to go for a week@@ end to R@@ ome ?
All expen@@ ses paid : hotel , transportation , food , break@@ fast , a contin@@ ental break@@ fast , everything .
Or a week@@ end in Paris ?
