At TED@@ 2009 , T@@ im Ber@@ ner@@ s-@@ Lee called for &quot; raw data now &quot; -- for governments , scientists and institutions to make their data open@@ ly available on the web . At TED University in 2010 , he shows a few of the interesting results when the data gets linked up .
